<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .invoice-box {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #718096;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>New Invoice Issued</h1>
        <p>Hello <strong>{{patientName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>A new invoice has been generated for your recent visit/service.</p>
        <div class="invoice-box">
            <p><strong>Invoice #:</strong> {{invoiceNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> â‚¹{{totalAmount}}</p>
            <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{dueDate}}</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button">View & Pay Invoice</a>
        </div>
        <p>Please ensure payment is made by the due date to avoid late fees.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Aarogentix. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>